" ∆ and ˚ are the results of OPTION-J and OPTION-K on  mac 
nnoremap ˚ <esc>:m .+1<CR>==
nnoremap ∆ <esc>:m .-2<CR>==
vnoremap ˚ :m '>+1<CR>gv=gv
vnoremap ∆ :m '<-2<CR>gv=gv
nnoremap yL yg_
